  <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 16px; color: var(--beeswax); line-height: 1.7;">Theosis is not an idea to agree with. It is a life to live. Start where the Fathers started: with the Jesus Prayer. Set aside five minutes today. Sit quietly. Breathe slowly. Repeat: <em>Lord Jesus Christ, Son of God, have mercy on me, a sinner.</em> Do not analyze it. Just pray it. Tomorrow, do it again.</p>
